  text: {fileID: 6274832859549691654}
  lines:
  - WOW.. a good burger like that made its way into Hell?
  - You're lucky Satan's letting me have this feast.. because I was gonna eat you.
  - And if you dont walk away right now and let me eat my  fucking burger in peace..
  - you are going to be my dessert.
